Definition: annual or perennial of tropical Asia having spikes of small white flowers and aromatic leaves
Example: one of the most important culinary herbs; used in salads, casseroles, sauces and some liqueurs
Synonyms: sweet_basil, Ocimum_basilicum, basil, annual, or, perennial, of, tropical, Asia, having, spikes, small, white, flowers, and, aromatic, leaves, one, the, most, important, culinary, herbs, used, in, salads, casseroles, sauces, some, liqueurs
Category: noun.plant
